<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title><%= title %> | Gendago</title>
	<link rel="preconnect" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net">
	<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.7/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-LN+7fdVzj6u52u30Kp6M/trliBMCMKTyK833zpbD+pXdCLuTusPj697FH4R/5mcr" crossorigin="anonymous">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/admin.css">
</head>
<body>
	<div class="container-fluid backoffice-shell">
		<div class="row min-vh-100">
			<%- include('partials/sidebar', { currentAdmin, page }) %>

			<main class="col-12 col-lg-9 col-xl-10 content-wrap">
				<% if (flashMessage) { %>
					<div class="alert alert-<%= flashMessage.type %> border-0 rounded-4 mb-4" role="alert"><%= flashMessage.text %></div>
				<% } %>

				<section class="glass-card p-4 p-xl-5 mb-4">
					<div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row justify-content-between align-items-md-end gap-3">
						<div>
							<p class="text-uppercase small fw-semibold text-secondary mb-2">Painel inicial</p>
							<h1 class="display-6 fw-semibold mb-2">Base do admin organizada para comecar a migracao</h1>
							<p class="text-secondary mb-0">A partir daqui voce pode concentrar usuarios, perfis, operacao e administracao sem misturar com a home experimental atual.</p>
						</div>
						<div class="text-md-end">
							<div class="small text-secondary">Ambiente atual</div>
							<div class="fw-semibold">FastAPI + PostgreSQL + Node web</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</section>

				<section class="row g-4 mb-4">
					<div class="col-12 col-md-4">
						<div class="metric-card h-100 p-4">
							<div class="metric-label mb-2">Modulo</div>
							<div class="metric-value">Usuarios</div>
							<p class="text-secondary mb-0">Base para login, perfis e controle de acesso por nivel.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="col-12 col-md-4">
						<div class="metric-card h-100 p-4">
							<div class="metric-label mb-2">Modulo</div>
							<div class="metric-value">Operacao</div>
							<p class="text-secondary mb-0">Listagens, filtros e fluxos administrativos usando layout consistente.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="col-12 col-md-4">
						<div class="metric-card h-100 p-4">
							<div class="metric-label mb-2">Status</div>
							<div class="metric-value">Pronto</div>
							<p class="text-secondary mb-0">Estrutura visual limpa, responsiva e pronta para evoluir por modulo.</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</section>

				<section class="row g-4">
					<div class="col-12 col-xl-7">
						<div class="glass-card p-4 h-100">
							<div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3">
								<h2 class="h4 mb-0">Sequencia recomendada</h2>
								<span class="badge rounded-pill text-bg-dark">Inicio</span>
							</div>
							<ol class="mb-0 text-secondary ps-3">
								<li class="mb-2">Subir autenticacao e sessao do backoffice.</li>
								<li class="mb-2">Modelar perfis master, admin e agente.</li>
								<li class="mb-2">Criar layout base de listagem, formulario e detalhes.</li>
								<li class="mb-2">Conectar os primeiros modulos a API Python atual.</li>
								<li>Portar o backend para Express por dominio, sem big bang.</li>
							</ol>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="col-12 col-xl-5">
						<div class="glass-card p-4 h-100">
							<h2 class="h4 mb-3">Modulos base</h2>
							<ul class="list-unstyled module-list mb-0">
								<li class="py-3">
									<div class="fw-semibold">Usuarios e perfis</div>
									<div class="text-secondary small">Controle de acesso, niveis e auditoria.</div>
								</li>
								<li class="py-3">
									<div class="fw-semibold">Cadastros principais</div>
									<div class="text-secondary small">Categorias, entidades e parametrizacoes.</div>
								</li>
								<li class="py-3">
									<div class="fw-semibold">Operacao e atendimento</div>
									<div class="text-secondary small">Fluxos do dia a dia com filtros e acoes seguras.</div>
								</li>
								<li class="py-3">
									<div class="fw-semibold">Relatorios e exportacoes</div>
									<div class="text-secondary small">Sempre com fila assíncrona quando o custo crescer.</div>
								</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>
				</section>
			</main>
		</div>
	</div>

	<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.7/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-ndDqU0Gzau9qJ1lfW4pNLlhNTkCfHzAVBReH9diLvGRem5+R9g2FzA8ZGN954O5Q" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>